    <note>Chen(1) Shi(21) [5064] Liu Zhi, WJ, 14.23a-23b (wife #3 of Guo(1) Shenxi [956}, surname Wu(3), who was 20 years younger than Shenxi and who married him after he had had six children by his first wives, which she raised. His second wife, surname Chen(1), is identified as the younger sister of Liu(2) Zhi's [8089] mother in this funerary inscription, i.e. the daughter of Chen(1) Xigu(3) [15143]. Surname Wu(3) died in 1068 at the age of 51. CBD, 3, 2133-4.</note>
